#: ../searching.rst:2
msgid "Search"
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:6
msgid ""
"The search is the tool of choice if you know what you are looking for but"
" not exactly where to find it."
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:10
msgid "Using the search icon"
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:12
msgid ""
"Among the icons in the top right corner you will find the search icon (a "
"magnifying glass)."
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:16
msgid ""
"Click it and a text input opens. Enter one or more words that are "
"contained in the document you are looking for."
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:20
msgid ""
"Submit your input by pressing enter. You are taken to the search results "
"page."
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:25
msgid "The search results"
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:29
msgid ""
"A list of results is displayed. The results most relevant to the search "
"are shown at the top of the list. Results will have a preview and/or "
"description where available."
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:33
msgid "There is an options menu that allows you to"
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:35
msgid "hide the previews to save some space on your screen"
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:36
msgid "change the sorting to have the most recent results at the top of the list."
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:40
msgid "Above the results list you can see how many results were found."
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:47
msgid "Filters"
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:51
msgid ""
"If the list is long you can narrow down your search by selecting filters "
"on the left. If, for example, you know the type of document you are "
"looking for then you can select it from the offered document types. The "
"result list is updated to reflect your selection."
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:58
msgid "Spell checking"
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:62
msgid ""
"Even if there is a typo in your search you can still find what you are "
"looking for. The search will suggest search words with similar spelling "
"to those you entered."
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:69
msgid "Alternate result views"
msgstr ""

#: ../searching.rst:73
msgid ""
"Several specialized results pages help you search for specific things, "
"for example people. They are accessible as tabs on the default results "
"page."
msgstr ""

